    <p>When I'm not coding or world-building, you'll usually find me:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Exploring the Inland Northwest in my RV with my wife, Gretchen, and our two dogs, Champ and Sophie.</li>
        <li>Tending to my garden or pressing flowers from the property.</li>
